    <text>
        <body>
            <div>
               
	<pb facs="liv_001509_0001" n="0001"/>
<lb/><opener><dateline><space extent="1" unit="words"/><placeName>Shupanga</placeName> <date when="1859-11-06"><subst><del>5</del><add place="over-text">6</add></subst> <choice><abbr>Nov</abbr><expan>November</expan></choice> 1859</date></dateline>  
<lb/><salute>My Dear <persName>D<hi rend="sup">r</hi> Kirk</persName></salute><space extent="2" unit="chars"/><hi rend="red" resp="#U">18</hi></opener>
<lb/><p>You will no
<lb/>doubt be disappointed
<lb/>at not finding us
<lb/>here - but there is
<lb/>no help for it as
<lb/>we are sinking.
<lb/><space extent="1" unit="chars"/>We waited at
<lb/>><placeName><settlement>Shamoara</settlement></placeName> till
<lb/>yesterday morning
<lb/><date when="1859-11-05">(5<hi rend="sup">th</hi></date>) - <space extent="2" unit="chars"/>We had
<lb/>made a good deal</p>
<lb/>
<lb/><cb rend="vertical"></cb><ab>I saw hardship for paper you see</ab><!-- Used coding manual, however this doesn't show up as verticle when I apply the transformation, so I'm not sure if it's correct? SF -->

	<pb facs="liv_001509_0002" n="0002"/>
<lb/><p rend="no-indent">of water and had
<lb/>to pump during the
<lb/>night while <persName>Rowe</persName>
<lb/>was away - <space extent="2" unit="chars"/>but - 
<lb/>lying in a still
<lb/>place the leak seemed
<lb/>to fill up. As you
<lb/>did not make
<lb/>your appearance
<lb/>I resolved to run
<lb/>down here for
<lb/>food for the crew - 
<lb/>and went to bed
<lb/>last night all night

	<pb facs="liv_001509_0003" n="0003"/>
<lb/>In the morning
<lb/>we found the <w>righ<gap extent="3" unit="chars"/></w>
<lb/>hand after hold <w>h<gap extent="3" unit="chars"/></w>
<lb/>forehold as well
<lb/>as stoke hole with
<lb/>a large quantity of
<lb/>water - This is
<lb/>in addition the the
<lb/>constant leak where
<lb/>the men sleep - Tried
<lb/>to stop the leak <unclear>in</unclear>
<lb/>after hold &amp; failed
<lb/>We have to pump
<lb/>every little while


	<pb facs="liv_001509_0004" n="0004"/><!-- pencil markings on the top of this page, but I didn't add them because I can't tell what they say- the numbers are maybe 2207? Can't properly make out the letters. SF -->
<lb/>the only chance of
<lb/>saving her is to get
<lb/>her beached without
<lb/>loss of time. We are
<lb/>Therefore cutting wood
<lb/>today &amp; will run down
<lb/>tomorrow to <placeName><geogName type="harbor">Kongone</geogName></placeName>
<lb/>I leave a whaler for
<lb/>you - You must just
<lb/>do the best you
<lb/>can in the case - I
<lb/>leave your letters - On
<lb/><unclear><choice><abbr>tom</abbr><expan>tomorrow</expan></choice></unclear> you will see how
<lb/>We have a small square
<lb/>box of tin for you <w>besid<gap extent="1" unit="chars"/><supplied>e</supplied></w>
<lb/>My brother is better
<lb/><space extent="1" unit="words"/><persName>David Livingstone</persName></p>

            </div>
